# RAG / data
# backend/chroma_db is deliberately COMMITTED (~9MB). The free-tier container has
# no persistent disk and only 512MB RAM, so re-embedding 1,232 docs on every cold
# start OOM'd it. Shipping the prebuilt index turns startup into a disk read.
# Rebuild after changing the data or the embedder:
#   cd backend && python -m app.rag.ingestion --reset

